name: Little Earths: Harvest Farm
description:
Tired of your dull life in the city?
Sick of sitting on a desk all day?

Come to Harvest Farm!

Nothing more relaxing than a day in Harvest Farm.
Water your favourite crops and harvest some berries!
Venture into the mines to collect some gems!
Chop some wood!
Milk your cow!

Move in to Harvest Farm TODAY!!
